strings:
<voice_0x0100171A><se_def>Prince Charmles: Honestly! Where has the Princess got to?
What's taking her so long!?

<voice_0x0100171D><se_def>Prince Charmles: What do you think you're doing!?
Are you trying to ruin my wedding!?

<voice_0x0100171E><se_def>Prince Charmles: I won't stand for it! Guards!
Get rid of him at once!
<voice_0x01001864><se_low>King Clavius: Wait! That will not be necessary!
<voice_0x01001865><se_low>King Clavius: <Cap><hero> has a right to be at this ceremony...

<voice_0x01001866><se_low>King Clavius: I, I have reconsidered...
You are the rightful groom, <hero>.

<voice_0x01001867><se_def>Prince Charmles: Father! How can you say such a thing!?
I'm the rightful groom!
<voice_0x01001868><se_low>King Clavius: Yesterday evening, the boy you see standing there gave me this ring.

<voice_0x01001869><se_def>Prince Charmles: W-What's that!?
Is it an Argon ring?
<voice_0x0100186A><se_def>Prince Charmles: I don't understand! Only members of the royal family who've passed the initiation should have a ring like that!

<voice_0x0100186B><se_low>King Clavius: This ring belonged to my elder brother...
It was Eltrio's ring...
<voice_0x0100186C><se_low>King Clavius: That boy is his son.
<voice_0x0100186D><se_low>King Clavius: It is only right that he should be the one to marry Princess Medea!
<voice_0x0100186E><se_def>Prince Charmles: No! I won't allow it!

<voice_0x0100186F><se_def>Prince Charmles: Princess Medea is promised to me!
So I'm the one who's going to be marrying her!
<voice_0x01001870><se_def>*: Pardon me for interrupting, Your Majesty.
<voice_0x01001871><se_def>*: I've just received word that the bride is now ready to make her appearance.

<voice_0x01001872><se_low>King Clavius: Open the doors!
Allow the bride to enter!
